article.description: — David Green scored 19 points off the bench and Amorie Archibald and Kenneth Lofton Jr. each scored 15 and Louisiana Tech walloped Texas Southern 87-60 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Green's 19 points catapults La. Tech past Texas Southern
article.linkText: Green's 19 points catapults La. Tech past Texas Southern
article.story: RUSTON, La. -- — David Green scored 19 points off the bench and Amorie Archibald and Kenneth Lofton Jr. each scored 15 and Louisiana Tech walloped Texas Southern 87-60 on Wednesday night. The Bulldogs (5-2) remained unbeaten in four games at home while keeping Texas Southern winless with seven defeats. Louisiana Tech built a 20-10 lead and never trailed in its second-largest margin of victory this season. The Bulldogs beat NAIA-member Jarvis Christian 91-61 on Nov. 15. John Walker III scored 15 points for the Tigers, and off the bench, Joirdon Karl Nicholas scored 13 and John Jones 10. ------
